<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.1">
<l>moymmām pūmpoḻil poykai mutalaic ciṟaippaṭṭu niṉṟa</l>
<l>kaimmāvuk karuḷ ceyta kārmukil pōlvaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇa</l>
<l>ṉemmā ṉaiccollip pāṭi yeḻuntum paṟantun tuḷḷātār</l>
<l>tammāl karumameṉ collīr taṇkaṭal vaṭṭattuḷ ḷīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kṛṣṇa, the one with a colour like a rain cloud who did grace to the hand animal</l>
<l>that stood held captive by the crocodile in the pond with [bee-]swarmed mango flower groves,</l>
<l>those who don’t frolic, rising and spreading in song, speaking about our lord</l>
<l>the deeds [done] by them are what, say, you who are in the circle [surrounded] by the cool sea?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
